1. Compounding Stake Growth Strategy

Best For: Long-term holders who want exponential RL1 growth over multiple cycles.

How It Works:
âœ… Stake 100% of unlocked RL1 every day instead of waiting for large unlocks.
âœ… Extend stake duration to 365 days for the maximum multiplier on re-staked RL1.
âœ… Over multiple cycles, re-staking compounds exponentially, leading to geometric growth.

